*Assessment*

In Eucalyptus 3.4, we introduced the [region condition key|https://github.com/eucalyptus/architecture/wiki/iam-3.4-cluster-policies#region-condition-key].  This currently doesn't work in Eucalyptus 4.2.0.
{code}
# euca-create-keypair gza-ghostface-killah > gza-ghostface-killah.pem -U http://compute.g-12-10.autoqa.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com:8773
euca-create-keypair: error (CreateKeyPairType): CreateKeyPair failed because: com.eucalyptus.auth.AuthException: Not authorized to create: key-pair by user: arn:aws:euare::001310814050:user/gza
{code}

